<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>New Achievement Unlocked!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #FF9800;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
        }
        .achievement {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid #FF9800;
        }
        .achievement-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #FF9800;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>ðŸŽ‰ Achievement Unlocked! ðŸŽ‰</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
        <p>Congratulations! You've just unlocked a new achievement in your sustainability journey.</p>

        <div class="achievement">
            <div class="achievement-icon">{{achievementIcon}}</div>
            <h2>{{achievementName}}</h2>
            <p>{{achievementDescription}}</p>
            
            <div style="margin-top: 15px; font-style: italic; color: #555;">
                <p>{{achievementImpact}}</p>
            </div>
            
            {{#if nextMilestone}}
            <div style="margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 15px;">
                <p><strong>Next milestone:</strong> {{nextMilestone}}</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px; color: #777;">
                Achieved on: {{dateEarned}}
            </div>
        </div>

        <p>Keep up the great work in reducing your carbon footprint!</p>
        <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">View All Achievements</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 